<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>eNPS 1H 2026 — Time Doctor</title>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/4.4.1/chart.umd.js"></script>
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
body{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif;background:#F5F6FA;color:#1A1A2E;line-height:1.6;}

.topbar{background:#fff;border-bottom:0.5px solid #E0E0E8;padding:0 2rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:56px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;}
.logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;}
.logo-dot{width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:6px;background:#185FA5;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}
.topbar-meta{font-size:12px;color:#9CA3AF;}

.wrap{max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;padding:2rem 1.5rem 4rem;}

.nav{display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:2rem;padding-bottom:1.25rem;border-bottom:0.5px solid #E8E8F0;}
.nav-btn{font-size:13px;padding:7px 16px;border-radius:20px;border:0.5px solid #D0D0DC;background:transparent;color:#6B7280;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;font-family:inherit;}
.nav-btn:hover{background:#F0F0F8;color:#1A1A2E;}
.nav-btn.act{background:#E6F1FB;color:#185FA5;border-color:#B5D4F4;font-weight:500;}

.view{display:none;animation:fadeIn .3s ease;}
.view.on{display:block;}
@keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}

/* HERO */
.hero{text-align:center;padding:2rem 0 1.75rem;}
.score-ring{position:relative;width:170px;height:170px;margin:0 auto 1.25rem;}
.score-num{position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);text-align:center;}
.score-big{font-size:50px;font-weight:500;color:#185FA5;line-height:1;}
.score-den{font-size:13px;color:#9CA3AF;margin-top:3px;}
.hero-h{font-size:21px;font-weight:500;color:#1A1A2E;margin-bottom:8px;}
.hero-s{font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.7;max-width:420px;margin:0 auto;}

.sl{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;color:#9CA3AF;letter-spacing:.07em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:12px;}
.card{background:#fff;border:0.5px solid #E0E0E8;border-radius:12px;padding:1.25rem;margin-bottom:12px;}
.mc{background:#F5F6FA;border-radius:8px;padding:1rem;text-align:center;}
.mc-v{font-size:28px;font-weight:500;color:#1A1A2E;line-height:1.1;}
.mc-l{font-size:12px;color:#6B7280;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.4;}
.g3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,minmax(0,1fr));gap:10px;margin-bottom:14px;}
@media(max-width:540px){.g3{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}}

.divider{border:none;border-top:0.5px solid #E8E8F0;margin:1.5rem 0;}

.who-bar{display:flex;height:22px;border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;margin:10px 0;}
.seg{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;color:#fff;}
.li{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:12px;color:#6B7280;margin-bottom:5px;}
.ld{width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:2px;flex-shrink:0;}

.explainer{background:#EEF4FF;border:0.5px solid #C7D7F4;border-radius:12px;padding:1.25rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;}
.ex-row{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;margin-bottom:12px;}
.ex-row:last-child{margin-bottom:0;}
.ex-icon{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;background:#DBEAFE;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;}
.ex-l{font-weight:500;font-size:13px;color:#0C447C;display:block;margin-bottom:3px;}
.ex-s{font-size:13px;color:#185FA5;line-height:1.65;opacity:.85;}

/* THEME CLUSTERS */
.theme-cluster{background:#fff;border:0.5px solid #E0E0E8;border-radius:12px;padding:1.25rem;margin-bottom:12px;transition:all .2s;}
.theme-cluster:hover{border-color:#B5D4F4;background:#FAFCFF;}
.theme-header{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:10px;}
.theme-icon{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;}
.theme-name{font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:#1A1A2E;}
.theme-tagline{font-size:12px;color:#6B7280;margin-top:1px;}
.theme-bar-wrap{flex:1;height:10px;background:#EEF0F5;border-radius:5px;overflow:hidden;}
.theme-bar{height:100%;border-radius:5px;transition:width .8s ease;}
.theme-score{font-size:14px;font-weight:500;width:34px;text-align:right;flex-shrink:0;}
.theme-stars{font-size:12px;flex-shrink:0;width:58px;}
.theme-body{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:8px;}
.theme-detail{font-size:12px;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.6;border-left:2px solid #EEF0F5;padding-left:10px;margin-top:6px;}
.theme-detail.green{border-left-color:#C0DD97;}
.theme-detail.amber{border-left-color:#F5C56E;}
.theme-detail.red{border-left-color:#F09595;}

/* PRIORITY BARS */
.prio-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:11px;}
.prio-label{font-size:13px;color:#1A1A2E;flex:0 0 200px;}
.prio-track{flex:1;height:10px;background:#EEF0F5;border-radius:5px;overflow:hidden;}
.prio-fill{height:100%;border-radius:5px;width:0%;transition:width .8s ease;}
.prio-pct{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:#6B7280;width:36px;text-align:right;flex-shrink:0;}

/* QUOTES */
.q-tab-bar{display:flex;gap:6px;margin-bottom:12px;}
.q-tab{font-size:13px;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:8px;border:0.5px solid #D0D0DC;background:transparent;color:#6B7280;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;font-family:inherit;}
.q-tab:hover{background:#F0F0F8;}
.q-tab.act{background:#F5F6FA;color:#1A1A2E;border-color:#AAAACC;font-weight:500;}
.qpanel{display:none;}.qpanel.on{display:block;}
.qcard{border-left:3px solid #E0E0E8;padding:.8rem 1rem;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;background:#F9FAFB;margin-bottom:10px;transition:transform .15s;}
.qcard:hover{transform:translateX(3px);}
.qt{font-size:13px;color:#1A1A2E;line-height:1.65;font-style:italic;}
.qcard.pos{border-left-color:#3B6D11;background:#F6FAF0;}
.qcard.imp{border-left-color:#185FA5;background:#EEF4FF;}

/* THEME TAG */
.q-theme-tag{display:inline-block;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:4px;margin-top:6px;}

/* NEXT BTN */
.next-btn{display:flex;justify-content:flex-end;margin-top:1.5rem;}
.next-btn button{font-size:13px;padding:8px 18px;border-radius:8px;border:0.5px solid #D0D0DC;background:#fff;color:#1A1A2E;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;transition:all .15s;font-family:inherit;}
.next-btn button:hover{background:#F0F0F8;}
.next-btn button svg{width:15px;height:15px;}

/* LEGEND */
.legend-note{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px;margin-top:12px;}
.legend-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:11px;color:#6B7280;}
.legend-dot{width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:2px;flex-shrink:0;}

/* THANK YOU */
.thank-card{text-align:center;padding:2.25rem 1.5rem;background:#fff;border:0.5px solid #E0E0E8;border-radius:12px;}

.footer{text-align:center;font-size:12px;color:#C0C0CC;padding:2rem 0;margin-top:1rem;}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="topbar">
  <div class="logo">
    <div class="logo-dot">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" width="16" height="16"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="6" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M5 8l2 2 4-4" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
    </div>
    <span style="font-size:15px;font-weight:500;color:#1A1A2E;">Time Doctor</span>
  </div>
  <div class="topbar-meta">eNPS 1H 2026 &nbsp;·&nbsp; For the whole team &nbsp;·&nbsp; May 2026</div>
</div>

<div class="wrap">

  <nav class="nav" aria-label="Dashboard sections">
    <button class="nav-btn act" onclick="goTo(0,this)">
      <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline;vertical-align:-2px;margin-right:4px;"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/></svg>
      Overview
    </button>
    <button class="nav-btn" onclick="goTo(1,this)">
      <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline;vertical-align:-2px;margin-right:4px;"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg>
      How we scored
    </button>
    <button class="nav-btn" onclick="goTo(2,this)">
      <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline;vertical-align:-2px;margin-right:4px;"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2z"/></svg>
      What you said
    </button>
    <button class="nav-btn" onclick="goTo(3,this)">
      <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline;vertical-align:-2px;margin-right:4px;"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 000-7.78z"/></svg>
      Thank you
    </button>
  </nav>

  <!-- VIEW 0: OVERVIEW -->
  <div id="v0" class="view on">
    <div class="hero">
      <div style="font-size:12px;color:#9CA3AF;margin-bottom:12px;">eNPS 1H 2026 &nbsp;·&nbsp; April 2026 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Time Doctor</div>
      <div class="score-ring">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 170 170" width="170" height="170" role="img" aria-label="Circular gauge showing our eNPS score animating up to 58 out of 100">
          <circle cx="85" cy="85" r="72" fill="none" stroke="#EEF0F5" stroke-width="13"/>
          <circle id="gauge-arc" cx="85" cy="85" r="72" fill="none" stroke="#185FA5" stroke-width="13"
            stroke-dasharray="452" stroke-dashoffset="452"
            stroke-linecap="round" transform="rotate(-90 85 85)" style="transition:stroke-dashoffset 1.4s ease;"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="score-num">
          <div class="score-big" id="score-count">0</div>
          <div class="score-den">out of 100</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-h">We asked. You answered. 💙</div>
      <div class="hero-s">125 of us took a few minutes to share how we really feel about working at Time Doctor. Here's everything we found — no jargon, just the truth.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="explainer">
      <div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:#0C447C;margin-bottom:14px;">First things first — what does that number mean?</div>
      <div class="ex-row">
        <div class="ex-icon"><svg width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#185FA5" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"/></svg></div>
        <div><span class="ex-l">One question started it all</span><span class="ex-s">We asked: "From 0–10, how likely are you to recommend Time Doctor as a great place to work?" The answers become our eNPS score.</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="ex-row">
        <div class="ex-icon"><svg width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#185FA5" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/></svg></div>
        <div><span class="ex-l">How the score works</span><span class="ex-s">People who scored 9 or 10 are Promoters. People who scored 6 or below are Detractors. We subtract % detractors from % promoters. Scores go from –100 to +100.</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="g3">
      <div class="mc"><div class="mc-v" id="cnt-people">0</div><div class="mc-l">people shared their thoughts</div></div>
      <div class="mc"><div class="mc-v" id="cnt-part">0%</div><div class="mc-l">of the whole team responded</div></div>
      <div class="mc"><div class="mc-v" id="cnt-avg">0</div><div class="mc-l">average score out of 10</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="who-bar" role="img" aria-label="Team vote distribution: 60% promoters, 38% passives, 2% detractors">
      <div class="seg" style="flex:60;background:#3B6D11;">60% love it here</div>
      <div class="seg" style="flex:38;background:#BA7517;">38% mostly positive</div>
      <div class="seg" style="flex:2;background:#A32D2D;">2%</div>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
      <div class="li"><span class="ld" style="background:#3B6D11;"></span>Promoters (scored 9–10) &nbsp;·&nbsp; 75 people &nbsp;·&nbsp; 60%</div>
      <div class="li"><span class="ld" style="background:#BA7517;"></span>Passives (scored 7–8) &nbsp;·&nbsp; 47 people &nbsp;·&nbsp; 38%</div>
      <div class="li"><span class="ld" style="background:#A32D2D;"></span>Detractors (scored 6 or below) &nbsp;·&nbsp; 3 people &nbsp;·&nbsp; 2%</div>
    </div>

    <div class="next-btn">
      <button onclick="goTo(1,document.querySelectorAll('.nav-btn')[1])">
        See how we scored
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- VIEW 1: HOW WE SCORED -->
  <div id="v1" class="view">
    <div class="sl">Score distribution — how everyone voted</div>
    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
      <div style="font-size:13px;color:#6B7280;margin-bottom:12px;">Hover any bar to see the exact count</div>
      <div style="position:relative;width:100%;height:160px;">
        <canvas id="scoreChart" role="img" aria-label="Bar chart of recommendation scores. Score 10 had the most responses at 45, followed by 8 with 31, 9 with 30, 7 with 16, and 6 with 3.">Score 6:3, 7:16, 8:31, 9:30, 10:45 responses.</canvas>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:11px;color:#9CA3AF;margin-top:8px;padding:0 4px;">
        <span>6 &nbsp;Detractor zone</span>
        <span>7–8 &nbsp;Passive zone</span>
        <span>9–10 &nbsp;Promoter zone</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sl">What the results look like by theme</div>
    <div style="font-size:13px;color:#6B7280;margin-bottom:14px;">We grouped the results into four themes based on what the survey covered. Hover each theme to see more detail.</div>

    <!-- THEME 1: Clear expectations -->
    <div class="theme-cluster">
      <div class="theme-header">
        <div class="theme-icon" style="background:#EAF3DE;">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3B6D11" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h11"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="theme-name">Clear expectations</div>
          <div class="theme-tagline">Knowing what's expected and where decisions come from</div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-left:auto;font-size:22px;font-weight:500;color:#3B6D11;">4.33<span style="font-size:12px;color:#9CA3AF;font-weight:400;"> / 5</span></div>
      </div>
      <div style="height:10px;background:#EEF0F5;border-radius:5px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:8px;">
        <div class="theme-bar" style="width:0%;background:#3B6D11;" data-w="86.6"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="theme-detail green">The team has a strong sense of what's expected of them and generally trusts the direction the company is headed. Context behind decisions scores slightly lower and is the area most people flagged as something to improve.</div>
    </div>

    <!-- THEME 2: Manager & leadership support -->
    <div class="theme-cluster">
      <div class="theme-header">
        <div class="theme-icon" style="background:#EAF3DE;">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3B6D11" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="theme-name">Manager &amp; leadership support</div>
          <div class="theme-tagline">Feeling backed by the people above you</div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-left:auto;font-size:22px;font-weight:500;color:#3B6D11;">4.48<span style="font-size:12px;color:#9CA3AF;font-weight:400;"> / 5</span></div>
      </div>
      <div style="height:10px;background:#EEF0F5;border-radius:5px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:8px;">
        <div class="theme-bar" style="width:0%;background:#3B6D11;" data-w="89.5"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="theme-detail green">This is one of our strongest areas. People feel supported by their managers and trust where the company is headed. It's consistently high across the team and came up frequently in the open-ended feedback as something people appreciate.</div>
    </div>

    <!-- THEME 3: Team connection -->
    <div class="theme-cluster">
      <div class="theme-header">
        <div class="theme-icon" style="background:#EAF3DE;">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3B6D11" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><line x1="23" y1="11" x2="17" y2="11"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="theme-name">Team connection</div>
          <div class="theme-tagline">Feeling part of the team even remotely</div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-left:auto;font-size:22px;font-weight:500;color:#BA7517;">4.31<span style="font-size:12px;color:#9CA3AF;font-weight:400;"> / 5</span></div>
      </div>
      <div style="height:10px;background:#EEF0F5;border-radius:5px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:8px;">
        <div class="theme-bar" style="width:0%;background:#BA7517;" data-w="86.2"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="theme-detail amber">Connection is positive overall, but it's the area people most want to see improve. More live moments — virtual and in-person — came up again and again. For a fully remote team spread across 40+ countries, this takes intentional effort.</div>
    </div>

    <!-- THEME 4: Workload & pay -->
    <div class="theme-cluster">
      <div class="theme-header">
        <div class="theme-icon" style="background:#FAEEDA;">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#854F0B" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="theme-name">Workload &amp; pay</div>
          <div class="theme-tagline">Feeling the work is sustainable and fairly rewarded</div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-left:auto;font-size:22px;font-weight:500;color:#BA7517;">3.93<span style="font-size:12px;color:#9CA3AF;font-weight:400;"> / 5</span></div>
      </div>
      <div style="height:10px;background:#EEF0F5;border-radius:5px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:8px;">
        <div class="theme-bar" style="width:0%;background:#BA7517;" data-w="78.5"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="theme-detail amber">Workload feels manageable for most. Pay is the clearest area of opportunity across the team — not so much the amounts themselves, but the lack of transparency around how pay decisions are made and what it takes to earn an increase.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="legend-note" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
      <span class="legend-item"><span class="legend-dot" style="background:#3B6D11;"></span>4.3 and above &nbsp;Going well</span>
      <span class="legend-item"><span class="legend-dot" style="background:#BA7517;"></span>3.8–4.2 &nbsp;Room to grow</span>
      <span class="legend-item"><span class="legend-dot" style="background:#A32D2D;"></span>Below 3.8 &nbsp;Needs attention</span>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>
    <div class="sl">What you want us to work on most &nbsp;·&nbsp; 116 responses</div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="prio-row"><span class="prio-label">Career growth</span><div class="prio-track"><div class="prio-fill" style="background:#185FA5;" data-w="36"></div></div><span class="prio-pct">36%</span></div>
